# HireSight Dashboard Templates - Complete Guide

**Created**: January 2026  
**Templates**: 2 dashboards (Personal + Company)  
**Status**: Production-Ready ‚úÖ

---

## üìÅ Files Created

1. **personal_dashboard.html** - Job seeker dashboard
2. **company_dashboard.html** - Recruiter/company dashboard

---

## üé® Design Overview

Both dashboards feature:
- **Gradient hero headers** with welcome message
- **Stats cards** (4 metrics) with color-coded borders
- **Two-column layout** (main content 2/3, sidebar 1/3)
- **Card-based design** with hover effects
- **Real-time data** integration
- **Empty states** with CTAs
- **Responsive** mobile design

---

## üë§ Personal Dashboard

### **Hero Section**
- Gradient background (primary ‚Üí secondary)
- Personalized welcome: "Welcome back, [Name]! üëã"
- Browse Jobs CTA button

### **Stats Cards (4)**
1. **Applications Submitted** (Blue)
   - Total this month
   - Weekly increase
   - Icon: Document

2. **Interviews Scheduled** (Cyan)
   - Upcoming count
   - Next interview date
   - Icon: Calendar

3. **Profile Views** (Gold)
   - Last 30 days
   - Percentage change
   - Icon: Eye

4. **Saved Jobs** (Purple)
   - Total saved
   - Link to view all
   - Icon: Bookmark

### **Main Content (Left Column)**

#### **1. Recent Applications**
Shows last 5 applications with:
- Company logo/avatar
- Job title & company name
- Application date (timesince)
- Status badge (color-coded):
  - Pending: Yellow
  - Reviewing: Blue
  - Interview: Purple
  - Offer: Green
  - Rejected: Red
- Location & salary
- "View details" link

**Empty State:**
- Icon
- "No applications yet" message
- "Browse Jobs" CTA button

#### **2. Recommended Jobs**
AI-matched jobs with:
- Company logo
- Match score badge (e.g., "85% Match")
- Save button (bookmark icon)
- Job details (type, location, salary)
- Description preview
- "View Details" and "Quick Apply" buttons
- Posted date

**Empty State:**
- "No recommendations yet"
- "Complete Profile" link

### **Sidebar (Right Column)**

#### **1. Profile Completion Card**
- Gradient background (primary ‚Üí secondary)
- Progress bar showing completion %
- Checklist of missing items:
  - Add profile photo
  - Add your skills
  - Add work experience
- "Complete Profile" CTA button
- Success state when 100%

#### **2. Quick Actions**
3 action cards:
- **Upload Resume** (Blue)
  - Upload icon
  - "Get AI-powered screening"
- **Search Jobs** (Cyan)
  - Search icon
  - "X new today"
- **Messages** (Gold)
  - Message icon
  - "X unread"

#### **3. Career Tips**
Tips card (light blue background):
- 3 helpful tips:
  - Optimize Your Profile
  - Apply Early
  - Customize Applications

